data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located in the adorable tucked away community of Hunters Lake! Built in 2020, this home is practically new, offering modern amenities and stylish finishes. features include:  large open kitchen boasting plenty of cabinet and countertop space, master bedroom with spacious walk-in closet and private bath, bonus room over the garage which would be perfect for creating a home office, media room, or additional living space. Location is key, and this house has it all. Situated in a perfect spot, it is conveniently close to local schools, downtown community amenities, and the coast guard base. This home is ready for its new owner, and to sweeten the deal, the seller is offering a generous $3,000 towards our buyers closing assistance! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this gorgeous house your new home.
